The purpose of this study is to compare the clinical efficacy of daily vs.

 3-day (MWF) buprenorphine/naloxone combination tablet administration and determine whether outcomes are improved when using a 3-day schedule in which all doses are ingested at the clinic vs.

 one in which take-home doses are given on intervening days.

